  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Minotaur Limb Replacement",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "弥诺陶洛斯肢体替换组件",
    "TraditionalChinese": "彌諾陶洛斯四肢替換零件"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A collection of salvaged components from a Sentinel Hardframe, reconditioned to fit the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid.<br><br>When installed alongside a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur Laser</span>, it transforms the mining laser into a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">powerful combat upgrade</span> with the ability to deal heavy damaged to <span class=\"name name-technology\">stunned</span> entities.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从一台护卫强化外壳上回收的构件，针对<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇进行了改装处理。<br><br>与<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯激光</span>一同安装后会给开采激光提供<span class=\"name name-stellar\">强大的升级组件</span>，能够对被<span class=\"name name-technology\">眩晕</span>的实体造成重创。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從巡警硬體結構中回收的一系列元件，經過翻新後用於<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇。<br><br>當和<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯雷射</span>一起安裝時，會將採礦雷射變化為<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強大的戰鬥升級</span>，擁有對處於<span class=\"name name-technology\">暈眩</span>狀態的存在體造成大量傷害的能力。"
  },
